Omolo, 31, joins BB Erzurumspor from Belgian club Cercle Brugge where he has spent the last four seasonsHis arrival comes at a time when the club is bottom of Turkey Super League side with 13 points from 18 matches Harambee Stars midfielder Johanna Omolo has joined Turkish topflight side Buyuksehir Belediye Erzurumspor. 
Omolo, 31, joins BB Erzurumspor from Belgian club Cercle Brugge where he has spent the last four seasons. 
His arrival comes at a time when the club is bottom of Turkey Super League with 13 points from 18 matches. 



