Omolo could make his debut on Thursday when the club hosts Alanyaspor in a Round 16 domestic cup match. 
BB Erzurumspor are based in Erzurumspor city and host their matches at the 23,700-seater Kazım Karabekir Stadium.  Bobi Wine has also revealed that his National Unity Platform (NUP) party has established an independent tallying centre to check against potential rigging. The move means Ugandans will cast their ballots amidst an internet blackout. President Donald Trump urges 'NO violence' and appeals for calm in the US as Congress debates his impeachment.